---
title: Savoury Chicken and Veggie Stir-Fry with Cashews and Garlic Rice
description: For those who don't shy away from spice, this chicken stir-fry packs a flavour punch and plenty of heat thanks to our Szechuan-style sauce! Toasted cashews finish off this dish for a culinary home run!
